Description: Hetzner Cloud SSH Management TUI
 A terminal-based user interface for executing SSH commands
 on Hetzner Cloud servers.
 .
 Features:
  - Multi-project support with API key management
  - Server filtering and selection
  - SSH private key management
  - Parallel SSH command execution
  - Easy configuration similar to AWS CLI
